C'mon Gene!

1st; I suspect that was deliberate so it could be powered and not on the internet.

2nd; it's things soldered together that shouldn't be, yet they somehow work. Call it a prototype, because it most certainly is.

3rd; when the article was written it was immense - and for a single device it's still an immense amount of traffic.

